          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1608551803728-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the spaghetti is cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> meat-free bacon lardons</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until golden and crispy all over</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1690275047113-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1690275047113-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1690275047113-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1690275047113-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1690275047113-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>crispy meat-free bacon</strong> to a bowl and return the pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>diced shallot </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once starting to soften, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min further or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1608551715413-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1608551715413-x400.jpg",
