            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the garlic is fragrant, reduce the heat to medium-low and add your<strong> creamy single soy</strong>, <strong>miso paste </strong>and<strong> remaining cider vinegar</strong></p><p>Tip: The miso paste adds an umami flavour to the sauce!</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened to a creamy consistency</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1608551742512-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1608551742512-x400.jpg",
