            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the<strong> cooked spaghetti</strong> and give everything a good mix up until the pasta is fully coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>plant-based spaghetti carbonara</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if the sauce is a little thick!</p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
